==========================================
FILES and DIR

#locate filename
---search perticular file

#mv filename newname
---to rename

#rm -rf =dir name=
---to remove non empty dir

#tar -xvf file.tar,gz
---to unzip file

#tar cvf filename.tar path/
---to create zip file

#diff file1 file2
---compare two files

===========================================
connections

#ssh-keygen
---to create ssh key

#ssh -T git@github.com
---to connect to github

#cat /.ssh/id_rsa.pub
---to see existing ssh key








(NOTE)
-h =human readable format
-s =total size
-n =number
-f =follow
-l =list
-a =all 
a* =begin with 'a'
*a*=contains 'a'

